    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2164820/extras/f75132644f36537d9cad18a1d2766b16.poster.avif?t=1770903119\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2164820/extras/f75132644f36537d9cad18a1d2766b16.webm?t=1770903119\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2164820/extras/f75132644f36537d9cad18a1d2766b16.mp4?t=1770903119\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Eons Away is a beautifully hand-drawn RPG set in the mystical land of Orya, where you'll embark on an epic quest to combat corruption across time. Immerse yourself in a rich narrative and engaging gameplay as you explore, socialize, and battle your way to uncover Orya's secrets.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2164820/extras/95bde4a3d5cf96da900e5ee3f45392fe.poster.avif?t=1770903119\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2164820/extras/95bde4a3d5cf96da900e5ee3f45392fe.webm?t=1770903119\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2164820/extras/95bde4a3d5cf96da900e5ee3f45392fe.mp4?t=1770903119\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Engaging Turn-Based Combat</h2>Engage in classic turn-based battles enhanced by a unique corruption system. Cleanse opponents from corruption or harness their power for strategic advantage.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2164820/extras/2fa54541b49cef83b632abef991c677b.poster.avif?t=1770903119\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2164820/extras/2fa54541b49cef83b632abef991c677b.webm?t=1770903119\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2164820/extras/2fa54541b49cef83b632abef991c677b.mp4?t=1770903119\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Soulpact System</h2>Forge soulpacts with summonable creatures. Each soulpact grants unique abilities, adding depth and variety to your combat strategy.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2164820/extras/9b6ae8b4b05f803efc3726fc00692c78.poster.avif?t=1770903119\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2164820/extras/9b6ae8b4b05f803efc3726fc00692c78.webm?t=1770903119\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2164820/extras/9b6ae8b4b05f803efc3726fc00692c78.mp4?t=1770903119\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Morality System</h2>Your actions shape your moral alignment, whether you choose righteousness or darker decisions. The morality system tracks your choices, impacting the story and character relationships.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2164820/extras/2ab4947b9a456a27e0261fd6f36cde6e.poster.avif?t=1770903119\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2164820/extras/2ab4947b9a456a27e0261fd6f36cde6e.webm?t=1770903119\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2164820/extras/2ab4947b9a456a27e0261fd6f36cde6e.mp4?t=1770903119\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Recruit Allies</h2>Meet and recruit unique allies, each with their own backstories and abilities. Develop these relationships to unlock new abilities, embark on special quests, and explore deeper personal stories.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2164820/extras/c0f359ba944fc7658bff3928a2dc5b7d.poster.avif?t=1770903119\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2164820/extras/c0f359ba944fc7658bff3928a2dc5b7d.webm?t=1770903119\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2164820/extras/c0f359ba944fc7658bff3928a2dc5b7d.mp4?t=1770903119\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Explore Orya</h2>Traverse the beautifully hand-drawn world of Orya, filled with lush forests, ancient temples, and vibrant landscapes. Discover hidden secrets, and delve into the rich lore that shapes this enchanting land.<br><br>Embark on a time-traveling journey with a diverse group of companions to save Orya from the encroaching darkness. Can you harness the power of the Eye of Orion and restore balance to the world? The fate of Orya is in your hands.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Traditional turn-based combat with a unique corruption system.<br></li><li>Cleanse corrupted creatures or harness their power.<br></li><li>Allies can become corrupted and receive combat penalties<br></li><li>A Morality system measures your moral alignment based on your actions.<br></li><li>Recruit and manage unique allies.<br></li><li>Explore and discover the secrets of Orya.</li></ul>",
